'''普利马克'''（'''Primark'''）是一家總部位於[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]][[都柏林|都柏林]]的服裝零售公司，在西歐和[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.idoleyes.com/fashion-blog/15050-primark-heads-america/ | publisher=Idol Eyes | title=Clothing store Primark opens in America | accessdate=23 April 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517155150/http://www.idoleyes.com/fashion-blog/15050-primark-heads-america/ | archive-date=2014-05-17 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>有多家分店。現為[[英聯食品|英聯食品]]的子公司。

==历史==
1962年6月在都柏林聖瑪麗街47號開業，1971年藉由在[[貝爾法斯特|貝爾法斯特]]市中心開業而把業務拓展到了英國，1973年在英格蘭開業。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://money.aol.co.uk/2014/03/23/the-rise-and-rise-of-primark/ | title = The rise and rise of Primark | publisher = AOL Money | accessdate = 25 March 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529032234/http://money.aol.co.uk/2014/03/23/the-rise-and-rise-of-primark/ | archive-date = 2014-05-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==問題==
2006年普利馬克加入[[道德貿易聯盟|道德貿易聯盟]]<ref>[http://www.ethicaltrade.org/Z/lib/2006/05/primark-press/index.shtml Primark joins Ethical Trading Initiative - Press Release - ETI] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071008102159/http://www.ethicaltrade.org/Z/lib/2006/05/primark-press/index.shtml |date=2007-10-08 }}</ref>，然而該公司在[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]的[[血汗工廠|血汗工廠]]一直沒有取締。2009年1月9日，一家供應商因為沒有為其員工提供英國法定最低工資且非法僱傭移民，而被道德貿易聯盟取消在普利馬克銷售產品的許可<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2009/jan/11/primark-ethical-business-living | work=The Guardian | location=London | title=Primark in storm over conditions at UK supplier | first=Dan | last=McDougall | date=11 January 2009 | accessdate=22 May 2010 | archive-date=2013-06-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625045403/http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2009/jan/11/primark-ethical-business-living | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年6月16日，BBC的編輯標準委員會（Editorial Standards Committee）發表文章稱普利馬克在[[印度|印度]]也有血汗工廠。儘管普利馬克隨後宣稱已經停止了和該工廠的印度供應商的聯繫，但編輯標準委員會指出這一聲明很可能並不屬實。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2004298/BBC-lose-prestigious-TV-award-faked-footage-child-labour-Primark-Panorama-expose.html | location=London | work=Daily Mail | first=Paul | last=Revoir | title=Shamed BBC could lose prestigious TV award over ‘faked footage of child labour' in Primark Panorama expose | date=17 June 2011 | accessdate=2014-05-14 | archive-date=2019-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829103004/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2004298/BBC-lose-prestigious-TV-award-faked-footage-child-labour-Primark-Panorama-expose.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年4月24日發生於[[達卡|達卡]]的[[2013年孟加拉国萨瓦区大楼倒塌事故|薩瓦區大樓倒塌事故]]造成了1,127死亡、2,438人受傷<ref>{{Citation | title = Bangladesh building collapse: An end to recovery efforts, a promise of a new start | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/14/world/asia/bangladesh-building-collapse-aftermath/ | last1 = Ahmed | first1 = Saeed | last2 = Lakhani | first2 = Leone | accessdate = 16 December 2013 | work = CNN | date = 14 June 2013 | archive-date = 2020-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201114001448/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/14/world/asia/bangladesh-building-collapse-aftermath | dead-url = no }}</ref>，普利馬克也在該大樓中擁有服裝生產廠<ref name=telegraph>{{Cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/bangladesh/10014778/Bangladesh-building-collapse-kills-at-least-82-in-Dhaka.html | work = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | accessdate = 24 April 2013 | date = 24 April 2013 | title = Bangladesh building collapse kills at least 82 in Dhaka | first = Dean | last = Nelson | location = London | archive-date = 2018-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180820172629/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/bangladesh/10014778/Bangladesh-building-collapse-kills-at-least-82-in-Dhaka.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=usatoday>{{Cite news | url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/04/24/bangladesh-building-collapse/2108727/ | work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]] | accessdate = 24 April 2013 | date = 24 April 2013 | title = At least 87 dead in Bangladesh building collapse | first = Julhas | last = Alam | archive-date = 2013-04-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130424125438/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/04/24/bangladesh-building-collapse/2108727/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外也是少數同意支付賠償金的公司之一<ref name=Ovi2013>{{Citation | title = Buyers' compensation for Rana Plaza victims far from reality | url = http://www.dhakatribune.com/business/2013/nov/17/buyers%E2%80%99-compensation-rana-plaza-victims-far-reality | year = 2013 | author = Ovi, Ibrahim Hossain | accessdate = 16 December 2013 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325223918/http://www.dhakatribune.com/business/2013/nov/17/buyers%e2%80%99-compensation-rana-plaza-victims-far-reality | archivedate = 2016年3月25日 }}</ref>。

